d.\n    [*]Each ink slot changes one color of the weapon, not all weapons use the three slots.\n    [*]The first time you put a weapon on the station, all the base paint will be removed for free!!!\n    [*]If when painting a weapon, you obtain a [i]perfectly generic item[/i](The green cube), post the [b]Weapon[/b] and the [b]mod[/b] it comes from in the \"Post Bugs HERE\" thread.\n[/list]\n\n[h1] Credits [/h1]\n[b]@Healthire[/b] - Developer of [url=http://community.playstarbound.com/resources/gun-assembly.2125/]Gun Assembly[/url], inspiration and base of this mod.\n[b]@Djinn[/b] - For the outstanding [i]Gun assembly station[/i] art.\n[b]@Inf_Wolf14[/b] - For the outstanding [i]Weapon painting station[/i] art.\n[b]@Mackinz[/b] - For [url=http://community.playstarbound.com/threads/offering-modpack-unpacking-services.121824/]Offering Modpack Unpacking Services[/url], where the original mod was unpacked.\n\n[h1] More info: [/h1]\nFor more info, please visit the forum thread: [url=http://community.playstarbound.com/resources/weapon-assembly.4277/]Link to the forum thread.[/url]\n",
